We are an energetic and dynamic band, bringing the best of rock and pop music to the world.
I'm a passionate singer-songwriter, telling stories through my music.
Ella Johnson is a talented singer-songwriter from New York, NY. Her soulful voice and heartfelt lyrics touch the hearts of her listeners.
The Night Riders is a dynamic band from Chicago, IL, known for their high-energy performances and versatile music spanning multiple genres.
Lucas Parker is a skilled guitarist and composer based in Los Angeles, CA. His instrumental music creates mesmerizing soundscapes.
Electric Pulse is a synth-driven band hailing from Seattle, WA. Their music takes you on an electrifying journey through retro-futuristic landscapes.
Olivia Turner is a talented country-pop singer-songwriter from Nashville, TN. Her heartfelt songs reflect the beauty of life and love.
Sunset Groove is a vibrant band from Miami, FL, known for their catchy melodies and infectious rhythms that get you moving.
Maxwell Reed is a talented singer-songwriter from Orland, who weaves poetic lyrics into his heartfelt acoustic melodies.
Aurora Beats is an electronic music producer and DJ from San Francisco, CA. Her beats create an ethereal atmosphere on the dance floor.
Sophie Martinez is a talented jazz vocalist and pianist from Los Angeles, CA. Her music evokes the classic sounds of the golden era.
Rising Tide is a rock band from Austin, TX, known for their anthemic songs and energetic live performances.
Leo Thompson is a talented singer-songwriter from Denver, CO, who enchants audiences with his soulful voice and introspective lyrics.
Galactic Fusion is a futuristic electronic duo from San Diego, CA, blending otherworldly sounds with infectious grooves.
Mia Roberts is a talented indie-pop singer-songwriter from Portland, OR, whose music captivates with its dreamy melodies and introspective lyrics.
Velvet Skies is a soulful band from Miami, FL, known for their smooth vocals and uplifting, R&B-infused tunes.
Noah Adams is a talented folk singer-songwriter from Austin, TX, whose heartfelt music is inspired by the beauty of nature and human connections.

Had a great time performing at a local open mic night last night! 🎤 Met some amazing fellow musicians and got to share our music with the audience. Looking forward to the next gig!
Working on some new song ideas in the studio today. Can't wait to share them with you all!
Just released a new single! 🎉 Check it out on Spotify and let me know what you think!
Jamming with the band in our garage studio. Love these creative sessions where we experiment with different sounds and genres. 🎸🥁
Excited to announce that we'll be playing at a local music festival next month! Can't wait to share our music with a larger audience.
Taking a break from gigs and spending some quality time in the studio, recording a few covers. Stay tuned for the release! 🎧
Just finished collaborating with an amazing singer on a new track. Can't wait for you all to hear it!
Feeling inspired after attending a live jazz performance last night. Time to incorporate some of those smooth melodies into my own music. 🎷🎶
Had an amazing time playing a surprise acoustic set at a local cafe this morning. Music really brightens up everyone's day! 🎤
Spent the weekend at a songwriting workshop. Feeling refreshed and full of new ideas! Can't wait to put them into songs.
Just released a music video for our latest single! Check it out on YouTube and let us know what you think!
Hitting the road for a mini-tour next week. Excited to visit new cities and meet music lovers from all around.
Just finished recording vocals for a new song. Can't wait to share this one with you all! 🎙️
Celebrating the release of our latest album with a virtual live stream concert. Join us on the journey! 🎤
Rehearsing for an upcoming gig. These pre-show jitters are always exciting! 🎸🎵
Just met with some fellow musicians to plan a collaborative music project. Can't wait to see it come to life!
Feeling grateful for all the support from my fans! You all keep me going. 🙏🎵
In the studio, working on some heavy riffs for our next metal track. Prepare for some headbanging! 🤘🎸
Just had a fantastic songwriting session. It's amazing how inspiration strikes at the most unexpected moments! 🎵✨
Performing at a local charity event tonight. So glad to be able to use music to make a positive impact.
Spent the afternoon in the recording booth laying down vocals. Can't wait for you all to hear these songs!🎙️
Releasing a new acoustic EP soon. Stripping back the production to let the raw emotions shine through. 🎵
